---

---

<section
  id="mission"
  class="bg-[#0a0a0a] py-28 lg:py-40 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Gold horizontal rule at top -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#c8a96e] to-transparent opacity-30"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Large ghost word -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-[-2rem] left-[-1rem] leading-none select-none pointer-events-none"
    style="font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:clamp(120px,18vw,240px); letter-spacing:-0.06em; color:transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.03); line-height:0.85;"
  >
    MISIÓN
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 relative">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <!-- Label column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 reveal">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-6 h-px bg-[#c8a96e]"></div>
          <span class="overline text-white/30">Nuestra Misión</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[13px] text-white/20 font-light leading-relaxed">
          El principio que guía cada decisión que tomamos como empresa.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Statement -->
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-9 lg:border-l lg:border-white/10 lg:pl-16 reveal reveal-delay-1"
      >
        <p
          class="font-display italic text-[clamp(1.8rem,3.8vw,3.2rem)] text-white/90 leading-[1.2] font-normal"
        >
          "Optimizar el uso eficiente de los recursos de las empresas,
          eliminando barreras de entrada y ayudando a pymes y organizaciones a
          expandir sus negocios mediante soluciones estratégicas, confiables y
          accesibles."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
